game is a little short, it took me about 5 hours to beat but even with that, i think its definitely worth the price. you can wait for it to go on sale if you dont wanna pay the full price. its just a wonderfully made game with an emotional story and lovable characters. 

if nothing else, its worth the price just to be the little companion and nuzzle the robots :))
